---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseHead 
  title="Help - Master Azerbaijani"
  description="Need assistance with your Master Azerbaijani learning journey? Find answers to common questions about lessons, pronunciation, accounts, and upcoming app features."
/>

<Header />

<main class="page-container about-page">
  <h1>Help & Guidance</h1>

  <p
    style="
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    "
  >
    Welcome! If you’re curious about Master Azerbaijani or want tips on learning your
    heritage language, you’re in the right place.
  </p>

  <ul
    style="
      text-align: left;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 20px auto 40px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    "
  >
    <li><strong>Getting started:</strong> How to make the most of your lessons once the app launches.</li>
    <li><strong>Learning tips:</strong> Fun ways to practice Azerbaijani with family or slip new words into everyday life.</li>
    <li><strong>Content questions:</strong> Ask about vocabulary, pronunciation, or cultural nuances.</li>
    <li><strong>Feedback & suggestions:</strong> Help shape the platform with your ideas and requests.</li>
  </ul>

  <p
    style="
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    "
  >
    For all inquiries, please email:
  </p>

  <p class="contact" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
    <a href="mailto:help@masterazerbaijani.com">help@masterazerbaijani.com</a>
  </p>

  <p
    style="
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      opacity: 0.9;
      line-height: 1.6;
    "
  >
    We’ll respond as quickly as possible. Your questions and ideas help us build a better
    platform for families everywhere!
  </p>
</main>

<Footer />
